HMR does not work for me unless add


if (module.hot) {
  module.hot.dispose(() => {});

  module.hot.accept();
}

I did this with typescript, and it was amazingly easy. Just point script src to an tsx file and create tsconfig.json with:

{
    "compilerOptions": {
      "jsx": "react",
      "allowSyntheticDefaultImports": true
    }
  }
